In this project, I build upon Tan et al. (https://chenhaot.com/pubs/winning-arguments.pdf) and their analysis of ChangeMyView, a subreddit with good-faith online discussions, to learn about human persuasion. 

system_instructions.txt contains the entire prompt for the Predict-Explain model. 

persuasion.ipynb contains the data wrangling code and API call.

visuals.ipynb contains the data visualization and exploratory work, along with some analysis. 
